*Welcome*
Welcome to Mobicents Bank IVR demo. If you are an existing customer press 1. For information on products and service press 2. To report loss of card press 3. To leave voice message press 4. At any time if you want to talk to customer service executive press 9 or to hangup press 0.

*Exisiting Customer*
Select from following 5 options. For Banking press 1. For credit card press 2. For online trading press 3. For loans press 4. To go back to previous menu press 8.


